OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDenmark set to ban         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flife-term prisoners from   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fnew romantic links         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Denmark's government has introduced a  
OL,6, bill that will ban prisoners serving   
OL,7, life sentences from entering into new  
OL,8, romantic relationships.                
OL,10,FUnder the new law prisoners will be    
OL,11,Flimited to contacting only those       
OL,12,Falready close to them for the first 10 
OL,13,Fyears of their incarceration.          
OL,15,FMinisters hope the ban will counter the
OL,16,Frise of 'groupies' of criminals.       
OL,18,FThe law follows the revelation that a  
OL,19,F17-year-old girl had fallen in love    
OL,20,Fwith the killer Peter Madsen.          
